'''Cyan Player Object Pool''' was an asset that can be used to assign a unique object to every player in the world.<ref>https://github.com/CyanLaser/CyanPlayerObjectPool</ref>. As of October 11th 2024, VRChat introduced native support for [[Player Object]]s in [[Open Beta]] and cyanlaser announced their intent to deprecate the CyanPlayerObjectPool asset<ref>https://x.com/CyanLaser/status/1844769943344312745</ref>.

